<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street Noon, CORRECTION,0331</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: Fixes ``employment'' in 5th graf</NOTE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market drifted in a narrow range today
amid concern over the interest-rate outlook.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 4.48 to 2,053.38
